      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about reyes syndrome but he's already got a bit of a stomach bug too so i was thinking maybe the aspirin would help with the inflammation? i just want him to be comfortable so he can sleep. is there any specific dose that is safe for his age if i just do it once?",
